properties.areaDesc: Flagler Beach to Volusia-Brevard County Line 0-20 nm; Volusia-Brevard County Line to Sebastian Inlet 0-20 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 3:25AM EST until January 11 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds increasing to around 20 knots beginning
Thursday, becoming southeast and gusting to 25 to 30 kt. Seas
building up to 6 to 8 feet.

* WHERE...Flagler Beach to Volusia-Brevard County Line 0-20 nm
and Volusia-Brevard County Line to Sebastian Inlet 0-20 nm.

* WHEN...From 4 AM Thursday to 7 PM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 4 AM THURSDAY TO 7 PM SATURDAY
